Anitec Image Technology Incsaid it filed a registration statement with the Securities andExchange Commission for a proposed offering of 60 mln dlrs inconvertible subordinated debentures.    Anitec said the proceeds will be used for acquisitions,joint ventures and other investments.    Anitec said the offering is being underwritten by SmithBarney, Harris Upham and Co, Donaldson Lufkin and JenretteSecurities, Salomon Inc &lt;SB>, and Mabon Nugent and Co. Reuter&#3;